*sane-backends-1.0.21-r1 (01 Sep 2010)

  01 Sep 2010; Patrick Kursawe <phosphan@gentoo.org>
  +sane-backends-1.0.21-r1.ebuild:
  Bug #322291: udev rules were overwritten by defaults.

  11 May 2010; Patrick Kursawe <phosphan@gentoo.org>
  sane-backends-1.0.21.ebuild:
  Fixed one of the SRC_URIs

